%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22My%2015-year-old%20son%20has%20his%20first%20girlfriend.%20Unlike%20when%20I%20was%20a%20teen%2C%20'hanging%20out'%20often%20just%20means%20talking%20on%20the%20phone%20at%20home.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222121%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Teenagers%20walking%20and%20holding%20hands%20while%20looking%20at%20their%20phones.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6659fdfc1cd3b17790421f39%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221414%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EStephanie%20Kaloi%20(not%20pictured)%20says%20dating%20is%20different%20now%20than%20when%20she%20was%20a%20teenager.%3Cp%3EGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EMy%20teenage%20son%20has%20his%20first%20girlfriend%20at%20the%20age%20of%2015.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EDating%20is%20much%20different%20now%20from%20when%20I%20was%20a%20teenager.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESometimes%2C%C2%A0%26quot%3Bhanging%20out%26quot%3B%20means%20talking%20on%20the%20phone%20while%20in%20different%20places.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20comes%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffiance-dated-teens-reconnected-proposal-decade-later-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eteen%20relationships%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20dating%2C%20I'm%20only%20too%20happy%20to%20admit%20that%20I%20don't%20know%20much%20about%20any%20of%20it.%20When%20my%20peers%20were%20hooking%20up%20at%20parties%20and%20stealing%20kisses%20in%20corners%20at%20school%20and%20having%20sex%2C%20I%20was%20fresh%20out%20of%20my%20boy%20band%20phase%20and%20into%20my%20rock%20'n'%20roll%20phase%2C%20busy%20planning%20a%20fantasy%20wedding%20to%20Oasis%20guitarist%20Noel%20Gallagher%20and%20being%20far%20too%20introverted%20to%20actually%20find%20and%20speak%20to%20a%20boy%20my%20own%20age.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20when%20my%20son%20began%20talking%20about%20girls%20a%20few%20years%20ago%2C%20I%20was%20surprised%20and%20intrigued%20%E2%80%94%20and%20also%20happy%20that%20he%20appeared%20to%20have%20the%20social%20ease%20I%20lacked%20and%20would%20likely%20enter%20into%20a%20rite%20of%20passage%20I%20missed%20out%20on%20entirely%20(though%20I've%20never%20been%20convinced%20that's%20a%20bad%20thing).%20I've%20only%20had%20two%20real%20relationships%20in%20my%20life%2C%20so%20I've%20also%20wondered%20just%20how%20much%20advice%20I%20can%20really%20give%20him%20about%20dating%20in%20the%20first%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%20that%20he%20has%20a%20girlfriend%2C%20it's%20so%20far%20turned%20out%20that%20he's%20not%20really%20looking%20for%20advice%20%E2%80%94%20after%20all%2C%20teens%20often%20think%20they%20know%20everything.%20However%2C%20he%20is%20happy%20to%20talk%20about%20his%20feelings%20and%20the%20nature%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fi-married-my-high-school-sweetheart-18-years-ago-2022-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehigh%20school%20relationships%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20first%20place%20(six%20months%20is%20a%20really%2C%20really%20long%20time%20for%20one%20to%20last%2C%20he%20says).%20Through%20those%20conversations%2C%20I've%20learned%20that%20while%20the%20core%20of%20teen%20love%20and%20feelings%20is%20still%20the%20same%20as%20it%20ever%20was%2C%20the%20way%20relationships%20between%20teens%20play%20out%20in%202024%20is%20pretty%20different.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c8759250-14ef-443c-acac-eb4590f8688c%5C%22%3ECommunication%20is%20different%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EObviously%2C%20cellphones%20and%20then%20smartphones%20changed%20the%20game%20in%20a%20lot%20of%20ways.%20For%20some%20of%20us%2C%20nearly%20everything%20we%20do%20is%20different%20because%20of%20a%20small%20device%20we%20can%20hold%20in%20our%20hands.%20We%20consume%20media%20differently%2C%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Fmental-health%2Fhow-to-focus%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edifferent%20attention%20spans%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20the%20way%20we%20communicate%20has%20changed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20been%20surprised%20to%20see%20how%20much%20my%20son's%20relationships%20(whether%20platonic%20or%20otherwise)%20have%20played%20out%20over%20his%20phone%20%E2%80%94%20texting%20and%20memes%20rule%20the%20day.%20It%20strikes%20me%20as%20different%20from%20what%20I%20remember%20at%20that%20age.%20Sure%2C%20I%20could%20definitely%20spend%20some%20time%20on%20the%20phone%2C%20but%20I%20also%20always%20wanted%20to%20physically%20spend%20time%20with%20friends%2C%20which%20doesn't%20seem%20to%20be%20as%20big%20of%20a%20priority%20with%20teens%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225af9a8e5-df58-4b09-88f5-ec9ef206c1c8%5C%22%3EHangouts%20aren't%20what%20they%20used%20to%20be%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20was%20a%20teen%2C%20I%20often%20wanted%20nothing%20more%20than%20to%20be%20away%20from%20my%20own%20home.%20I%20was%20constantly%20at%20my%20best%20friend's%20house%2C%20or%20we%20were%20driving%20around%20aimlessly%2C%20listening%20to%20music%2C%20doing%20anything%20that%20meant%20we%20were%20together.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20son%20and%20his%20friends%20often%20%26quot%3Bhang%20out%26quot%3B%20for%20hours%20at%20a%20time%2C%20too%2C%20but%20they%20do%20so%20separately%2C%20at%20their%20own%20homes%2C%20often%20over%20the%20phone%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fonline-games-activities-to-try-with-long-distance-friends-family-2020-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethrough%20an%20online%20game%3C%2Fa%3E.%20This%20is%20likely%20a%20consequence%20of%20the%20prolonged%20pandemic%2C%20and%20forced%20separation%20has%20turned%20into%20a%20preference.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20true%20for%20his%20relationship%20as%20well.%20While%20they%20might%20see%20each%20other%20once%20a%20week%20or%20once%20every%20other%20week%2C%20neither%20of%20them%20seems%20to%20mind%20%E2%80%94%20and%20maybe%20that's%20a%20good%20thing%20after%20all.%20Who%20wants%20two%20bored%20teens%20who%20are%20attracted%20to%20one%20another%20hanging%20out%20alone%20for%20hours%20with%20nothing%20to%20do%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220d8b5a9d-279e-401f-9bcf-a963c3d68717%5C%22%3EHaving%20a%20relationship%20is%20(apparently)%20novel%20in%20the%20first%20place%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20surprised%20to%20learn%20that%20teen%20relationships%20are%20something%20of%20a%20dying%20trend%20in%20the%20United%20States%2C%20though%20I'm%20probably%20not%20the%20only%20one.%20According%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsrcd.onlinelibrary.wiley.com%2Fdoi%2F10.1111%2Fcdev.12930%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20study%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20American%20teens%20are%20less%20likely%20than%20previous%20generations%20to%20take%20part%20in%20so-called%20%26quot%3Badult%26quot%3B%20activities%2C%20like%20being%20employed%2C%20drinking%20alcohol%2C%20and%20dating.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20data%20was%20echoed%20by%20findings%20from%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.americansurveycenter.org%2Fresearch%2Fgeneration-z-and-the-transformation-of-american-adolescence-how-gen-zs-formative-experiences-shape-its-politics-priorities-and-future%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESurvey%20Center%20on%20American%20Life%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20reported%20only%2056%25%20of%20Gen%20Z%20adults%20(the%20generation%20that%20my%20son%20belongs%20to)%20said%20they%20had%20any%20kind%20of%20romantic%20relationship%20in%20their%20teens%2C%20a%20drop%20from%2069%25%20of%20millennials%2C%2076%25%20of%20Gen%20X%2C%20and%2078%25%20of%20baby%20boomers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20reason%20I%20was%20surprised%20to%20find%20teens%20aren't%20dating%20as%20much%20is%20that%20my%20son%20and%20his%20friends%20have%20been%20talking%20about%20being%20in%20relationships%20for%20years%20%E2%80%94%20well%20before%20they%20were%20actually%20ready%20to%20do%20so%20%E2%80%94%20and%20I%20just%20assumed%20all%20teens%20were%20the%20same%20way.%20Since%20most%20of%20his%20friends%20have%20also%20begun%20relationships%20or%20already%20had%20their%20first%20break-up%2C%20it%20seems%20they%20also%20have%20a%20pretty%20laid-back%20approach%20to%20how%20long%20a%20relationship%20should%20last%20at%20this%20stage%20in%20their%20lives%2C%20which%20makes%20that%20fervor%20from%20long%20ago%20pretty%20funny%20to%20look%20back%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhatever%20does%20or%20doesn't%20happen%20with%20my%20son's%20relationship%2C%20it's%20fun%20to%20go%20on%20the%20ride%20with%20him%2C%20largely%20as%20an%20observer%2C%20and%20to%20witness%20him%20beginning%20to%20step%20into%20a%20safe%20version%20of%20adulthood%20before%20he's%20really%20out%20in%20the%20world.%20As%20his%20mom%2C%20it's%20always%20my%20priority%20to%20hear%20and%20support%20him%20no%20matter%20what%20and%20to%20help%20him%20navigate%20each%20path%20he%20takes%20%E2%80%94%20and%20this%20one%20is%20no%20different.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fteenage-son-first-girlfriend-2024-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717325581000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6659fe0fcc442a2f676cc183%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fteenage-son-first-girlfriend-2024-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22My%2015-year-old%20son%20has%20his%20first%20girlfriend%20and%20dating%20is%20different%20from%20when%20I%20was%20a%20teenager.%20Most%20communication%20is%20done%20over%20texting.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Stephanie%20Kaloi)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fteenage-son-first-girlfriend-2024-6%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Zelensky%20accuses%20Russia%20and%20China%20of%20undermining%20summit%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717324975000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbra