ts%20first%203G%20phone%20%E2%80%94%20with%20a%20color%20screen%2C%20camera%2C%20and%20faster%20data%20connectivity%2C%20an%20effort%20to%20enter%20the%20advanced%20phone%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20released%20a%20USB%20modem%20in%202006%2C%20which%20could%20be%20plugged%20into%20computers%20to%20access%20the%20internet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBy%20the%20late%202000s%2C%20Huawei%20reached%20a%20series%20of%20financial%20milestones.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224192%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Huawei%20Shenzen%20office%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6658d5b7d0b8e1c832ca6c9e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222760%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDespite%20some%20rough%20years%2C%20Huawei%20carried%20on%20through%20the%202000s.%3Cp%3ESTR%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBetween%202008%20and%202009%2C%20contract%20sales%20increased%20by%2046%25%20%E2%80%94%20most%20of%20which%20came%20from%20overseas%20%E2%80%94%20and%20generated%20close%20to%20%2423.3%20billion%20in%20revenue%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Farticle%2FidUSN01324096%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EReuters%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20company%20was%20also%20seeking%20to%20expand%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EFollowing%20the%20success%20of%20its%20smartphones%2C%20Huawei%20expanded%20into%20wearable%20devices%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225248%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Richard%20Yu%2C%20CEO%20of%20Huawei's%20consumer%20business%20group%2C%20launches%20the%20new%20watch%20GT2%20at%20the%20Convention%20Center%20in%20Munich%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6658ceacd0b8e1c832ca62dd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223576%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESince%20the%20success%20of%20its%20cellphones%2C%20Huawei%20has%20ventured%20into%20more%20smart%20devices.%3Cp%3EMichael%20Dalder%2FReuters%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202015%2C%20the%20company%20released%20the%20Huawei%20watch%2C%20which%20combined%20typical%20watch%20functions%20with%20modern%20smartwatch%20features.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBy%202019%2C%20the%20telecom%20giant%20seemed%20to%20be%20leading%20the%205G%20revolution%20for%20faster%20wireless%20connection%20globally%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226112%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ren%20Zhengfei%20huawei%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5c6bccc3262898527629cde5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224383%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EHuawei%20founder%20Ren%20Zhengfei%20remains%20CEO.%3Cp%3EAP%20Photo%2FVincent%20Yu%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20of%20February%202019%2C%20the%20company%20had%20more%20than%2030%20contracts%20for%205G%20and%20deployed%20more%20than%2040%2C000%205G%20stations%20globally%2C%20the%20LA%20Times%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.latimes.com%2Fprojects%2Fla-fi-tn-huawei-5g-trade-war%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereported%2C%20%3C%2Fa%3Edemonstrating%20its%20global%20influence.%20Huawei%20execs%20claimed%20that%20the%20company%20was%20ahead%20of%20America's%20most%20advanced%20providers%20in%20developing%20the%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EHuawei%20employees%20reportedly%20say%20the%20pay%20is%20stellar%20despite%20the%20tough%20work%20environment.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225972%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Huawei%20sign%20with%20people%20walking%20by%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6658cf7b1cd3b1779041bc1e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223987%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EHuawei%20is%20known%20for%20its%20intense%20work%20culture.%3Cp%3ETingshu%20Wang%2FReuters%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20former%20employee%20said%20workers%20get%20juicy%20bonuses%20that%20%26quot%3Busually%20exceed%20our%20base%20salary%26quot%3B%20for%20finishing%20projects.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20just%20obscene%20amounts%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20employee%20told%20the%20LA%20Times%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20employee%20told%20the%20outlet%20that%20Huawei%20gives%20employees%20the%20option%20to%20buy%20company%20shares%20if%20they%20hit%20performance%20goals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20compensation%20for%20workers%20seemed%20to%20have%20offset%20the%20company's%20so-called%20%26quot%3Bwolf%20culture%2C%26quot%3B%20where%20some%20were%20expected%20to%20take%20on%20the%20work%20of%20three%20people%2C%20sources%20told%20the%20LA%20Times.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20performance%20reviews%2C%20Chinese%20staff%20are%20reportedly%20ranked%20A%2C%20B%2C%20C%2C%20or%20D%2C%20where%20workers%20are%20pitted%20against%20one%20another%20to%20succeed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWorkers%20who%20received%20a%20score%20of%20A%20got%20double%20the%20bonuses%20employees%20who%20scored%20B%20got%2C%20a%20Shenzhen-based%20employee%20told%20the%20Times.%20Those%20who%20scored%20C%20%E2%80%94%20which%2010%25%20of%20staff%20must%20get%20%E2%80%94%20for%20two%20consecutive%20years%20were%20fired.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EHuawei's%20smartphones%2C%20one%20of%20its%20most%20successful%20consumer%20products%2C%20are%20now%20a%20rival%20to%20Apple's%20iPhone%20in%20China%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20customer%20tries%20out%20Huawei%20Mate%2060%20smartphone%20at%20a%20Huawei%20flagship%20store%20on%20September%204%2C%202023%20in%20Shanghai%2C%20China.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64fea036a39a1b00190cd7e9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222800%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Huawei%20Mate%2060%20rivals%20the%20latest%20iPhone.%3Cp%3EWang%20Gang%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20introduced%20Ascend%2C%20its%20first%20line%20of%20smartphones%2C%20in%202010%20in%20a%20move%20to%20enter%20the%20global%20smartphone%20market%20following%20the%20rel