E%3Cp%3EIn%202023%2C%20the%20founders%20of%20Lazo%2C%20a%20platform%20specializing%20in%20relationship%20loyalty%20tests%2C%20contacted%20me.%20They%20found%20me%20on%20TikTok%20and%20asked%20if%20I%20would%20offer%20my%20service%20through%20their%20platform.%20I%20agreed.%20Now%2C%20I%20do%20loyalty%20tests%20for%20a%20living%20and%20help%20even%20more%20women%20than%20when%20I%20did%20it%20on%20my%20own.%20I%20mostly%20test%20boyfriends%20but%20have%20tested%20about%20five%20husbands%20since%20I%20started.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20users%20come%20to%20Lazo%20needing%20a%20loyalty%20test%2C%20they%20can%20pick%20the%20'tester'%20they%20want%20based%20on%20location%2C%20hobbies%2C%20interests%2C%20hair%20color%2C%20and%20other%20things%20they%20think%20their%20significant%20other%20might%20be%20into.%20There%20are%20roughly%20400%20testers%20on%20the%20platform.%20Loyalty%20testers%20have%20different%20prices%2C%20depending%20on%20the%20price%20they%20set%20for%20themselves.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20have%20a%20set%20fee%20of%20%2470%20for%20a%20%26quot%3Bmission.%26quot%3B%20Lazo%20takes%20%2421%2C%20and%20I%20keep%20%2449.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDepending%20on%20how%20many%20I%20can%20handle%2C%20I%20do%2015%20to%2020%20missions%20a%20week.%20Sometimes%2C%20a%20mission%20can%20take%20a%20little%20over%20an%20hour%2C%20but%20others%20can%20take%20up%20to%20a%20week%20if%20not%20more.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnfortunately%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20the%20girls%20who%20come%20to%20Lazo%20are%20usually%20right%20about%20their%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsmoothie-receipt-tipped-woman-off-to-cheating-boyfriend-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echeating%20boyfriends%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a214b55e-c0f1-421c-a50c-87d78a6071c6%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EOnce%20I%20take%20on%20a%20mission%2C%20I%20get%20to%20work%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20hiring%20me%2C%20users%20tell%20me%20what%20social%20media%20platform%20their%20boyfrie