C%2Fa%3E%20suggest%20the%20plans%20have%20been%20scaled%20back%2C%20the%202.4km%20still%20due%20to%20be%20built%20will%20be%20the%20largest%20linear%20city%20in%20existence%20if%20it%20is%20completed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20concept%2C%20linear%20living%20is%20nothing%20new.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20ambitious%20but%20hardly%20revolutionary%2C%26quot%3B%20Anirban%20Adhya%2C%20a%20Professor%20of%20Architecture%20and%20Urban%20Design%20at%20Lawrence%20Technological%20University%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20Industrial%20Revolution%2C%20many%20urban%20planners%20looked%20to%20alternative%20city%20layouts%20to%20tackle%20booming%20populations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Spanish%20architect%20Arturo%20Soria%20is%20widely%20credited%20with%20designing%20the%20first%20linear%20city%2C%20%26quot%3BLa%20Ciudad%20Lineal%2C%26quot%3B%20in%201882%20on%20the%20outskirts%20of%20Madrid.%20Around%20forty%20years%20later%2C%20in%201924%2C%20renowned%20Swiss-French%20architect%20Le%20Corbusier%20offered%20another%20radical%20alternative%20with%20his%20%26quot%3BVille%20Radieuse%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20linear%2C%20ordered%20metropolis%20full%20of%20green%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Soviet%20urbanist%20Mikhail%20Okhitovich%20was%20sent%20to%20a%20gulag%20in%201930%20for%20his%20%26quot%3Beconomically%20crippling%26quot%3B%20proposal%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsocks-studio.com%2F2012%2F07%2F14%2Fmikhail-okhitovich-and-the-disurbanism%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etransform%20the%20city%20of%20Magnitogorsk%3C%2Fa%3E%20into%20eight%20ribbon-like%20strips%20converging%20on%20a%20factory.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20has%20been%20common%20for%20urban%20planners%20to%20argue%20for%20a%20new%20future%20as%20a%20reaction%20to%20what%20they%20claim%20to%20be%20an%20'unsustainable%3B'%20existing%20situation%20of%20their%20time.%20The%20Line%20in%20Neom%20is%20no%20different%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Adhya.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20revol