e%20Line's%20linear%20form%20would%20make%20it%20accessible%20and%20facilitate%20the%20integration%20of%20renewable%20energy%20sources%20along%20its%20entire%20length.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221980%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Neom%20construction.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66509bc620abc1efe8fd4e4d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22990%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EConstruction%20of%20Neom.%3Cp%3ENeom%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20she%20said%20its%20goals%20may%20be%20exaggerated%2C%20Lovgreen%20believes%20the%20vision%20of%20The%20Line%20is%20admirable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20challenges%20us%20to%20rethink%20urban%20design%20and%20discover%20new%20ways%20to%20make%20cities%20efficient%2C%20livable%2C%20and%20sustainable.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20could%20set%20a%20trailblazing%20example%20for%20how%20to%20use%20AI%20to%20improve%20sustainability%20and%20energy%20efficiency%2C%20something%20US%20urban%20planners%20should%20replicate%2C%20Lovgreen%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20focus%20on%20convenience%20and%20services%20being%20within%20reach%20also%20shows%20promise%2C%20Adhya%20said%2C%20pointing%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-freedom-cities-build-housing-conservatives-scoff-at-leftist-plan-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esuccessful%20examples%20already%20underway%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20cities%20like%20Paris%20and%20Portland.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20%26quot%3Bsmaller%20chunks%20and%20pieces%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20linear%20structure%20of%20The%20Line%20could%20work%2C%20Adhya%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2254f67557-c933-4746-bf46-7f190715c720%5C%22%3E'Bland%20and%20monotonous'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20some%20practical%20sides%20of%20the%20structure%20have%20potential%2C%20all%20experts%20BI%20spoke%20to%20saw%20fundamental%20issues%20with%20the%20lived%20experience%20inside%20linear%20cities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Line%20could%20be%20a%20fascinating%20place%20to%20visit%20and%20experience%2C%20but%20I'm%20still%20unsure%20of%20whether%20humans%20are%20designed%20to%20live%20in%20such%20a%20rigid%20and%20prescriptive%20structure%2C%26quot%3B%20Lovgreen%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Line%20is%20formed%20of%20modules%20that%20can%20each%20house%2080%2C000%20people%2C%20able%20to%20move%20about%20through%20a%20horizontal%20and%20vertical%20transport%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Line%2C%20NEOM%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64353ff22588f70018ce4071%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThis%20publicity%20image%20shows%20a%20design%20for%20'The%20Line'%2C%20a%20part%20of%20the%20planned%20Saudi%20Arabian%20desert%20megacity%20in%20NEOM.%3Cp%3ENeom%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCompared%20to%20other%20urban%20designs%20like%20grid%20layout%2C%20radial%20layout%2C%20ring%20layout%2C%20or%20some%20combination%20of%20these%2C%20human%20experience%20in%20a%20strictly%20linear%20urban%20development%20can%20lack%20interest%20and%20variation%2C%26quot%3B%20explained%20Adhya.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCertain%20parts%20of%20the%20city%20could%20become%20too%20far%20and%20segregated.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20repetition%20of%20infrastructure%20and%20kit-of%20parts%20would%20be%20%26quot%3Bbland%20and%20monotonous%2C%26quot%3B%20lacking%20the%20unique%20character%20that%20other%20cities%20offer%2C%20said%20Lovgreen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUltimately%2C%20the%20psychological%20impact%20of%20living%20in%20such%20a%20regimented%20environment%20may%20affect%20residents'%20well-being%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20type%20of%20structure%20is%20not%20only%20monotonous%2C%20but%20can%20limit%20social%20cohesion%2C%20according%20to%20John%20Gold%2C%20a%20professor%20of%20Urban%20Historical%20Geography%20at%20Oxford%20Brookes%20University.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLinear%20cities%20are%20an%20extreme%20form%20of%20urban%20dispersal%20%E2%80%94%20community%20development%20and%20social%20cohesion%20still%20need%20centrality%2C%26quot%3B%20Gold%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20challenge%20in%20Neom's%20design%20is%20its%20over-reliance%20on%20technology%20and%20the%20public%20transport%20system%2C%20experts%20said.%20If%20something%20went%20wrong%2C%20the%20entire%20system%20would%20crumble%2C%20they%20warned.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMost%20cities%20have%20network%20redundancy%2C%20where%20multiple%20options%20are%20available%20if%20a%20specific%20connection%20or%20intersection%20is%20blocked.%20A%20linear%20city%20may%20not%20have%20this%20capability%2C%26quot%3B%20explained%20Lovgreen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22NEOM%20Saudi%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5f61d46b323fc4001e0d6808%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20site%20of%20NEOM%20in%20Tabuk%20Province%2C%20Saudi%20Arabia.%3Cp%3ENEOM%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ELastly%2C%20in%20spite%20of%20The%20Line's%20proclamations%20of%20sustainability%2C%20its%20huge%20mirrored%20walls%20could%20be%20harmful%20ecologically%20both%20in%20terms%20of%20unnecessary%20heat%20gain%20within%20the%20structure%20as%20well%20as%20being%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fneom-the-line-mirrored-tower-birds-kill-saudi-arabia-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edetrimental%20for%20the%20migratory%20flight%20paths%20of%20billions%20of%20birds%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20big%20issue%2C%20according%20to%20Gold%2C%20is%20%26quot%3Bwho%20would%20actually%20want%20to%20live%20in%20such%20a%20'city'%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20schemes%2C%20and%20the%20Saudi%20one%20is%20a%20classic%20example%2C%20map%20out%20a%20hi-tech%20