t%20things%20change%20in%20life%2C%20and%20eventually%2C%20I%20decided%20marriage%20was%20right%20for%20me.%20I%20met%20my%20now%20husband%2C%20a%20handsome%20bohemian%20Italian%20artist%2C%20during%20my%20first%20summer%20living%20in%20Italy%20almost%2010%20years%20ago.%20We%20immediately%20fell%20in%20love%20and%20after%20a%20year%20of%20dating%2C%20we%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoving-in-together-relationship-dynamic-change-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Emoved%20in%20together%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20living%20together%20for%20six%20months%2C%20the%20topic%20of%20children%20came%20up.%20We%20had%20spoken%20about%20it%20before%2C%20but%20that%20evening%20was%20different.%20We%20talked%20about%20having%20children%2C%20how%20many%20we%20wanted%20(two)%2C%20and%20when%20we%20might%20start%20trying.%20Then%2C%20while%20we%20were%20talking%2C%20the%20topic%20of%20marriage%20came%20up.%20I%20honestly%20don't%20even%20remember%20who%20brought%20it%20up.%20As%20we%20kept%20talking%20late%20into%20the%20evening%2C%20I%20casually%20asked%2C%20%26quot%3Bell%2C%20do%20you%20think%20we%20should%20get%20married%3F%26quot%3B%20to%20which%20Vito%2C%20my%20now%20husband%20replied%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20want%20to%20do%20whatever%20makes%20you%20happiest.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERight%20then%20and%20there%2C%20on%20a%20random%20night%20in%20January%20of%202017%20we%20became%20engaged.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22bccef840-fd0a-4b13-9642-71f2d64e86f1%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20was%20surprised%20when%20I%20changed%20my%20mind%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20think%20what%20it%20comes%20down%20to%20is%2C%20I%20am%20more%20traditional%20and%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkid-came-out-nonbinary-parent-role-changed-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Econservative%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20than%20I%20originally%20thought.%20In%20my%20head%2C%20I%20always%20thought%20that%20I%20wanted%20to%20be%20a%20mom%20and%20didn't%20care%20if%20I%20was%20married%20to%20the%20father%20of%20my%20children.%20That%20was%20in%20theory.%20But%20once%20reality%20set%20in%20that%20I%20was%20with%20the%20man%20that%20I%20actually%20wanted%20to%20have%20children%20with%2C%20it%20felt%20different%2C%20and%20it%20started%20to%20feel%20like%20it%20just%20made%20sense%20to%20me%20to%20be%20married%20as%20well.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20fact%2C%20I%20didn't%20want%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3Enot%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cspan%3E%20be%20married%20to%20the%20father%20of%20my%20babies%20%E2%80%94%20I%20wanted%20to%20get%20married%20first%2C%20and%20then%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cspan%3Ehave%20children.%20It%20was%20almost%20a%20shocking%20revelation%20to%20myself%2C%20since%20I%20never%20thought%20it%20mattered%20to%20me.%20It%20turned%20out%2C%20in%20the%20back%20of%20my%20head%2C%20it%20did.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222777%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Black%20and%20white%20photo%20of%20Caroline%20Chirichella%20with%20her%20husband%20and%20daughter.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F665a07c21cd3b177904227bf%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222083%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECaroline%20Chirichella%20feels%20as%20though%20she%20was%20meant%20to%20be%20a%20mother.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20Caroline%20Chirichella%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2274ba7833-2f18-4bcc-88dc-452a50d7ff29%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20don't%20always%20enjoy%20everything%20that%20comes%20with%20being%20a%20'wife'%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMy%20husband%20and%20I%20have%20been%20together%20going%20on%2010%20years%2C%20and%20have%20been%20married%20for%20a%20little%20over%20seven.%20It's%20strange%2C%20but%20sometimes%2C%20I%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwant-be-tradwife-traditional-wife-marriage-homemaker-life-meaning-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Elove%20being%20a%20wife%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20having%20that%20title.%20I%20actually%20like%20cleaning%20the%20house%20and%20making%20meals%20specially%20for%20my%20husband.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20there%20are%20times%20that%20I%20really%20don't%20enjoy%20it.%20I%20need%20my%20space.%20I%20need%20my%20privacy.%20There%20are%20moments%20when%20I%20don't%20want%20to%20have%20to%20tell%20my%20husband%20everything%20that%20I'm%20doing%20%E2%80%94%20not%20because%20I'm%20doing%20something%20I%20shouldn't%20be%2C%20but%20because%20sometimes%2C%20it%20feels%20like%20too%20much%20work%20to%20have%20explain%20everything%20that%20I%20have%20going%20on%2C%20especially%20as%20a%20mom%20of%20two%20children%20under%20the%20age%20of%20five%20who%20is%20also%20running%20my%20own%20business.%20It%20just%20sometimes%20feels%20like%20too%20much%20to%20have%20to%20be%20a%20wife.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225623ad9a-a10f-448b-82fb-013ac5f0abd7%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20I've%20always%20loved%20being%20a%20mom%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20I%20love%20being%20a%20mom%20more%20than%20anything%20in%20this%20world.%20It's%20my%20calling.%20I%20truly%20feel%20I%20was%20put%20on%20this%20earth%20to%20be%20a%20mother.%20My%20children%20fill%20my%20life%20with%20such%20joy%20and%20fun.%20Yes%2C%20it's%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmiss-being-single-mom-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ehard%20being%20a%20mom%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20and%20some%20days%20are%20absolute%20chaos%2C%20but%20it's%20what%20I'm%20best%20at.%20Being%20a%20mom%20is%20my%20happy%20and%20safe%20place.%20It's%20a%20love%20that%20is%20like%20no%20other.%3C%2Fspan%