e%20works%20as%20a%20digital%20marketer%20on%20the%20influencer%20marketing%20team%20at%20PMG.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221168%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Arielle%20Francois%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F665a2dc6d0b8e1c832caf059%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22876%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFrancois%20works%20for%20PMG.%3Cp%3ESkylar%2FCourtesy%20of%20Arielle%20Francois%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFrancois%20is%20among%20the%20many%20people%20who%20moved%20to%20the%20Dallas%20metro%20area%20in%202022.%20Nearly%2091%2C600%20more%20people%20moved%20in%20than%20out%20of%20the%20Dallas%20area%20from%20elsewhere%20in%20the%20US%20during%20the%20period%20of%20July%201%2C%202021%2C%20and%20June%2030%2C%202022%2C%20data%20from%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.census.gov%2Fdata%2Ftables%2Ftime-series%2Fdemo%2Fpopest%2F2020s-total-metro-and-micro-statistical-areas.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECensus%20Bureau%3C%2Fa%3E%20showed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20find%20Dallas%20is%20up%20and%20coming%2C%26quot%3B%20Francois%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrancois%20sees%20several%20positives%20to%20living%20in%20Dallas%2C%20including%20more%20visibility%20and%20opportunities%20as%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiktok.com%2F%40ari.frcs%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econtent%20creator%3C%2Fa%3E.%20With%20more%20and%20more%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-millennials-baby-boomers-jobs-employment-changes-glassdoor-report-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGen%20Zers%20moving%20into%20full-time%20employment%3C%2Fa%3E%20while%20baby%20boomers%20enter%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-x-baby-boomers-savings-cant-afford-retirement-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eretirement%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20leave%20behind%20full-time%20jobs%2C%20Francois%20talked%20to%20BI%20about%20advice%20for%20anyone%20uprooting%20their%20lives%20to%20move%20somewhere%20new.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225a982ed7-4b10-461c-ba70-3b6f71a68bdc%5C%22%3ELeveraging%20social%20media%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFrancois%20advised%20people%20who%20are%20moving%20to%20make%20sure%20they%20do%20their%20research.%20She%20has%20also%20found%20social%20media%20can%20be%20useful%20for%20moving%20%E2%80%94%20not%20only%20to%20see%20what%20life%20is%20like%20in%20the%20place%20you%20are%20heading%20to%20but%20as%20a%20way%20to%20reach%20out%20to%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20Francois%20said%20she%20used%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsmartcitylocating.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESmart%20City%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20find%20a%20place%20to%20live.%20She%20said%20it's%20a%20service%20where%20you%20connect%20with%20a%20%26quot%3Blocator%20to%20help%20you%20find%20the%20apartment%20that%20you%20want%20in%20your%20desired%20location.%26quot%3B%20Francois%20said%20she%20learned%20about%20this%20%26quot%3Bthrough%20a%20Dallas%20local%20I%20reached%20out%20to%20on%20social%20media%20while%20doing%20my%20research.%20This%20highlights%20the%20importance%20of%20seeking%20advice%20from%20locals%20and%20leveraging%20social%20media%20during%20the%20moving%20process.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20feel%20like%20social%20media%20is%20the%20perfect%20place%20for%20you%20to%20discover%20a%20city%20because%20you%20have%20a%20ton%20of%20content%20creators%20who%20are%20creating%20amazing%20content%20about%20the%20good%2C%20the%20bad%2C%20pretty%2C%20the%20ugly%20about%20the%20city%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeyond%20scrolling%20through%20social%20media%20posts%20and%20apartment%20sites%2C%20there%20are%20also%20rent%20and%20costs%20to%20think%20about.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20recommend%20budgeting%20and%20saving%20as%20much%20as%20possible%20%E2%80%94%20your%20future%20self%20will%20appreciate%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20for%20other%20Gen%20Zers%20living%20on%20their%20own%20for%20the%20first%20time.%20She%20added%20that%20can%20include%20not%20spending%20too%20much%20on%20furniture%20and%20thrifting%20items.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMoving%20to%20a%20new%20city%20can%20also%20mean%20figuring%20out%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-make-friends-as-adult-moving-cities-nyc-la-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehow%20to%20make%20friends%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Francois%20said%20not%20to%20forget%20others%20may%20be%20new%20to%20the%20area%20and%20seeking%20new%20friends.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMaking%20friends%20can%20be%20intimidating%2C%20but%20there%20are%20often%20many%20social%20groups%20on%20Facebook%20or%20platforms%20like%20The%20Nudge%20that%20organize%20social%20events%20and%20provide%20lists%20of%20activities%20in%20your%20city%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BSocial%20media%20is%20also%20a%20great%20way%20to%20meet%20new%20people%20and%20discover%20local%20events.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2272a4fee4-eb04-456e-a00b-1b36d36f69c0%5C%22%3EHow%20her%20life%20in%20Dallas%20compares%20to%20Florida%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20I%20would%20definitely%20say%20that%20my%20favorite%20part%20about%20the%20city%20is%20how%20helpful%20and%20open%20everyone%20is%2C%26quot%3B%20Francois%20said%20about%20Dallas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20going%20out%20with%20her%20colleagues%20is%20one%20of%20her%20favorite%20things%20to%20do%20in%20the%20area.%20For%20instance%2C%20she%20went%20to%20her%20first-ever%20baseball%20game%20with%20her%20coworkers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrancois%20has%20also%20found%20Dallas%20a%20good%20city%20to%20live%20in%20as%20a%20content%20creator%20compared%20to%20Miami.%20%26quot%3BThe%20visibility%20I%20got%20in%20South%20Florida%20was%20very%20limited%20just%20because%20there%20were%20so%20many%20other%20creatives%20in%20terms%20of%20models%20and%20artists%20and%20content%20creators%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20in%20Dallas%2C%20she%20feels%20she%20gets%20more%20visibility%20as%20a%20creator%2C%20%26quot%3Bwhich%20has%20actually%20resulted%20in%20much%20more%20opportunities%20for%20me%20here%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BFor%20example%2C%20I%20get%20invited%20to%20a%20ton%20of%20Dallas%20creator%20events%20with%20some%20brands%20that%20I%20personally%20use%2C%20and%20I%20just%20actually%20feel%20like%20a%20creator%20here%20just%20because%20I%20get%20that%20visibility%20as%20a%20creator%2C%20and%20so%20I'm%20treated%20like%20I'm%20a%20creator.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20Francois%20said%20she%20feels%20it's%20more%20affordable%20to%20live%20in%20Dallas%20than%20South%20Florida%20for%20someone%20her%20age.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EAccording%20to%20Zillow%20data%20at%20the%20time%20of%20reporting%2C%20the%20median%20rent%20for%20a%20one-bedroom%20property%20is%20%242%2C700%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.zillow.com%2Frental-manager%2Fmarket-trends%2Fmiami-fl%2F%3Fbedrooms%3D1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMiami%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20around%20%241%2C400%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.zillow.com%2Frental-manager%2Fmarket-trends%2Fdallas-tx%2F%3Fbedrooms%3D1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDallas%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrancois%2C%20who%20hasn't%20had%20roommates%20while%20living%20in%20Dallas%2C%20paid%20nearly%20%241%2C600%20a%20month%20in%20rent%2C%20including%20some%20fees%2C%20for%20her%20first%20apartment%20in%20the%20city.%20She%20moved%20earlier%20this%20year%20to%20a%20new%20building%2C%20where%20she%20pays%20over%20%241%2C800%20a%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20she%20has%20%26quot%3Beverything%20you%20could%20possibly%20need%2C%26quot%3B%20at%20her%20current%20place.%20%26quot%3BTo%20me%2C%20it%20was%20worth%20the%20increase%20in%20rent%2C%20but%20I%20know%20not%20everyone%20would%20necessarily%20agree.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20she%20finds%20that%20Dallas%20is%20quieter%20than%20Miami.%20%26quot%3BI%20remember%20when%20I%20lived%20there%2C%20I%20would%20say%2C%20'I%20live%20where%20you%20vacation%2C'%26quot%3B%20Francois%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20want%20to%20party%2C%20you%20go%20to%20Florida%2C%20whereas%20I%20don't%20think%20if%20you%20want%20to%20party%2C%20you%20would%20think%20of%20Dallas%20as%20the%20go-to%20city%20for%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20Francois%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20I'm%20totally%20OK%20with%20living%20somewhere%20like%20that%20because%20of%20where%20I'm%20at%20mentally%2C%20professionally%2C%20and%20all%20of%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20she%20does%20miss%20being%20close%20to%20the%20beach%2C%20a%20personal%20pro%20for%20her%20of%20living%20in%20Dallas%20is%20seeing%20the%20differences%20in%20seasons%20and%20the%20changing%20weather.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBecause%20I%20grew%20up%20in%20the%20Caribbean%20islands%2C%20I'm%20very%20used%20to%20sunny%20weather%20and%20just%20basically%20summer%20weather%20all%20year%20long%2C%26quot%3B%20Francois%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%2C%20I%20actually%20like%20that%20in%20Dallas%20I'm%20able%20to%20see%20the%20seasons%20change.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20misses%20the%20Haitian%20community%20in%20Florida%20and%20says%20that%20if%20she's%20craving%20Haitian%20food%2C%20she%20won't%20really%20find%20it%20in%20Dallas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBecause%20South%20Florida%20is%20so%20close%20to%20Haiti%2C%20you'll%20find%20a%20huge%20population%20of%20Haitians%20in%20South%20Florida%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%20when%20I%20moved%20to%20Florida%2C%20I%20didn't%20feel%20like%20I%20was%20too%20far%20away%20from%20home%20because%20there%20were%20so%20many%20Haitian%20restaurants%2C%20so%20many%20Haitian%20churches.%20There's%20even%20Little%20Haiti%20in%20South%20Florida.%20So%2C%20Haitian%20culture%20is%20very%20present%20there.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGiven%20the%20mix%20of%20things%20she%20misses%20about%20South%20Florida%20and%20the%20perks%20of%20being%20in%20Dallas%2C%20Francois%20said%20she%20would%20tell%20her%20past%20self%20who%20was%20getting%20ready%20to%20move%20that%2C%20%26quot%3BIt's%20normal%20to%20be%20nervous%20because%20change%20is%20uncomfortable%26quot%3B%20and%20it's%20an%20uneasy%20feeling%20to%20experience%20this%20new%20chapter%20in%20life%20alone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20fine%20to%20feel%20how%20you%20feel%2C%20but%20if%20only%20you%20knew%20what%20was%20on%20the%20other%20side%20of%20all%20of%20that%20fear%20and%20anxiety%2C%20you%20would%20quickly%20wipe%20your%20tears%20and%20get%20to%20packing%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EHave%20you%20moved%20out%20of%20Florida%20or%20moved%20to%20Texas%3F%20Share%20your%20moving%20experience%20with%20this%20reporter%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Amhoff%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Emhoff%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoving-from-florida-to-dallas-texas-pros-cons-2024-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717321022000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6658e75ed0b8e1c832ca8123%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoving-from-florida-to-dallas-texas-pros-cons-2024-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Arielle%20Francois%20thinks%20Dallas%20is%20quieter%20than%20Miami%20and%20is%20more%20affordable%20than%20living%20in%20South%20Florida%20for%20someone%20her%20age.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Madison%20Hoff)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoving-from-florida-to-dallas-texas-pros-cons-2024-6%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22EXID's%20Hani%20announces%20marriage%20with%20longtime%20bf%22%2C%22cont