ide%20money%20for%20community%20improvement%20projects%20that%20could%20benefit%20others%20long-term.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20try%20to%20nickel%20and%20dime%20myself%20if%20it%20doesn't%20make%20me%20happy%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20want%20to%20be%20a%20billionaire%20by%20any%20stretch%20of%20the%20imagination%2C%20but%20there%20are%20things%20that%20I%20would%20like%20to%20do%20after%20I've%20shifted%20my%20mind.%20I%20would%20love%20to%20create%20a%20park%20one%20day%2C%20for%20example%2C%20in%20my%20area%20that%20has%20all%20different%20equipment.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20schedules%20one-on-one%20time%20with%20his%20kids%2C%20plays%20basketball%20twice%20a%20week%2C%20and%20makes%20time%20for%20tennis%20or%20golf%20with%20friends%2C%20all%20of%20which%20take%20precedence%20in%20his%20schedule.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20considering%20his%20%26quot%3Bfinal%26quot%3B%20retirement%2C%20he%20said%20he%20plans%20to%20work%20as%20long%20as%20he%20enjoys%20it.%20While%20he%20doesn't%20want%20to%20be%20a%20%26quot%3Bfull-time%20parent%26quot%3B%20and%20needs%20work%20to%20keep%20him%20going%2C%20he's%20increasingly%20trying%20to%20pick%20up%20and%20drop%20off%20his%20kids%20at%20school%20and%20attend%20their%20sporting%20events.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20long%20as%20I'm%20able%20to%20continue%20to%20take%20enough%20vacations%2C%20travel%2C%20do%20some%20of%20the%20things%20that%20I've%20always%20liked%20doing%20locally%2C%20and%20do%20some%20of%20my%20hobbies%20a%20few%20times%20a%20year%2C%20I'm%20in%20a%20pretty%20good%20spot%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAre%20you%20part%20of%20the%20FIRE%20movement%20or%20living%20by%20some%20of%20its%20principles%3F%20Reach%20out%20to%20this%20reporter%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Ansheidlower%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Ensheidlower%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C