ckquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EDear%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FINCIndia%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40INCIndia%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20thank%20you%20for%20your%20concern.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FEaseMyTrip%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40EaseMyTrip%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20halted%20Maldives%20bookings%20from%20January%208th%20until%20today.%20Some%20bookings%20did%20occur%20between%20May%2016th%20-%2026th%2C%20but%20we%20took%20immediate%20action%20and%20got%20them%20removed.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnWhy%20focus%20only%20on%20us%3F%20Are%20you%20not%20aware%20of%20other%20Chinese-owned%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F0NrHtoEIxy%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F0NrHtoEIxy%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Nishant%20Pitti%20(%40nishantpitti)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fnishantpitti%2Fstatus%2F1796895708681048461%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJune%201%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20emphasized%20the%20company's%20dedication%20to%20a%20nationalistic%20approach%2C%20stating%2C%20%26quot%3BWe've%20been%20serving%20for%20the%20last%2016%20years%20without%20any%20foreign%20investments.%20Yes%2C%20you're%20right%2C%20nothing%20is%20permanent--the%20money%20will%20come%20and%20go.%20But%20our%20nationalistic%20approach%20will%20never%20change.%20By%20the%20way%2C%20we%20are%20here%20for%20the%20long%20haul%2C%20and%20it's%20not%20easy%20for%20us%20to%20go.%20Hope%20you%20understand.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20response%20came%20after%20Kerala%20Congress%20questioned%20EaseMyTrip%20on%20X%2C%20highlighting%20the%20company's%20earlier%20decision%20to%20remove%20Maldives%20from%20their%20platform%20as%20a%20show%20of%20support%20for%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20party%20questioned%20the%20resumption%20of%20bookings%2C%20asking%2C%20%26quot%3BA%20couple%20of%20months%20ago%2C%20online%20travel%20aggregator%20%40EaseMyTrip%20made%20a%20nationalistic%20move%20by%20removing%20the%20Maldives%20as%20a%20destination%20from%20their%20flight%20and%20hotel%20booking%20platform%20to%20support%20PM%20Modi.%20Now%20they%20have%20quietly%20resumed%20booking%20to%20Maldives.%20We%20are%20wondering%20what%20happened.%20Is%20it%20a%20sign%20of%20something%3F%20Is%20money%20more%20important%20than%20PM%20Modi%3F%20Money%20will%20come%20and%20go%2C%20and%20so%20is%20PM%20Modi!%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecently%2C%20screenshots%20circulating%20on%20social%20media%20showed%20Maldives%20bookings%20available%20on%20EaseMyTrip%2C%20prompting%20questions%20about%20whether%20the%20company%20had%20reversed%20its%20boycott.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENishant%20Pitti%20clarified%20on%20social%20media%20that%20the%20boycott%20remains%20in%20place%20and%20any%20future%20changes%20would%20be%20formally%20announced.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEaseMyTrip%20initially%20halted%20operations%20in%20Maldives%20in%20January%20after%20three%20Maldivian%20ministers%20made%20derogatory%20comments%20about%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20following%20his%20visit%20to%20Lakshadweep.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20suspension%20of%20flight%20bookings%20to%20the%20Maldives%2C%20made%20in%20solidarity%20with%20the%20government%2C%20impacted%20240%2C000%20annual%20bookings%20through%20their%20platform.%20Prashant%20Pitti%2C%20co-founder%20of%20EaseMyTrip%2C%20noted%20a%20significant%2040%20per%20cent%20surge%20in%20bookings%20last%20year%20compared%20to%20the%20previous%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20boycott%2C%20EaseMyTrip%20recently%20reported%20its%20highest-ever%20earnings%20before%20interest%2C%20taxes%2C%20depreciation%2C%20and%20amortization%20(EBITDA)%20for%20the%20fiscal%20year%202024%2C%20amounting%20to%20Rs%202%2C282%20million%2C%20reflecting%20a%2019%20percent%20year-on-year%20growth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20company's%20consolidated%20reven