king%20with%20Sunny%20once%20again.%20Their%20previous%20collaborations%20include%20'Dillagi'%2C%20'Farz'%2C%20'Yeh%20Raaste%20Hain%20Pyaar%20Ke'%2C%20and%20'The%20Hero'%2C%20although%20they%20didn't%20share%20scenes%20in%20'Heroes'.%20Reflecting%20on%20their%20reunion%2C%20Zinta%20expresses%20her%20fondness%20for%20the%20Deol%20family%20and%20her%20enjoyment%20of%20working%20on%20the%20film.%20She%20appreciates%20Sunny's%20dual%20role%20as%20actor%20and%20director%2C%20recalling%20his%20support%20during%20their%20first%20collaboration%20in%20'Farz'.%20Humorously%2C%20Zinta%20describes%20her%20character%20in%20'Lahore1947'%20as%20'characterless'%2C%20jokingly%20attributing%20it%20to%20her%20eagerness%20for%20the%20proper%20promotional%20materials.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I%20tracked%20all%20the%20ads%20I%20received%20in%20a%20day%20%E2%80%94%20here's%20what%20I%20saw%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%227639%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ads%20graphic%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6659f7f2cc442a2f676cbe7a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225707%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMost%20of%20the%20ads%20I%20saw%20were%20on%20social%20media%20and%20I%20didn't%20mind%20them.%20%3Cp%3Echokkicx%2FGetty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EI%20tracked%20all%20the%20ads%20I%20saw%20in%20a%20day%20and%20counted%20over%20130.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESome%20ad%20settings%20can%20be%20adjusted%2C%20but%20control%20over%20frequency%20remains%20limited%20across%20many%20platforms.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EI%20didn't%20mind%20most%20ads%20because%20they%20either%20catered%20to%20my%20interests%20or%20were%20easy%20to%20tune%20out.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAds%20have%20become%20so%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fadvertising-data-importance-consumers-shopping-trends-digitial-retail-media-tv-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eembedded%20in%20everyday%20activities%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20media%20consumption%20that%20you%20may%20not%20even%20notice%20how%20often%20you%20run%20into%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20my%20editor%20asked%20me%20to%20track%20all%20the%20ads%20I%20saw%20in%20a%20day%2C%20I%20wasn't%20sure%20how%20it%20would%20go.%20Prior%20to%20this%20experiment%2C%20I%20hadn't%20paid%20close%20attention%20to%20how%20often%20an%20ad%20or%20sponsored%20content%20floated%20before%20my%20eyes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-get-sponsored-on-instagram%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWhile%20the%20words%20%26quot%3Bsponsored%26quot%3B%20may%20show%20up%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20a%20video%20or%20image%20you%20scroll%20past%20on%20social%20media%2C%20the%20font%20is%20often%20small%20and%20if%20the%20content%20is%20successfully%20targeting%20you%2C%20you%20may%20not%20even%20notice.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20missed%20a%20few%20ads%20during%20this%20process%2C%20especially%20on%20sites%20where%20I%20was%20focused%20on%20getting%20the%20answer%20I%20was%20searching%20for.%20But%20based%20on%20what%20I%20did%20catch%2C%20I%20spotted%20over%20130%20ads%20in%20a%20single%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELet's%20dive%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2279509f49-699e-4b35-8c12-d71e31b2474d%5C%22%3EYour%20settings%20can%20(sometimes)%20make%20a%20difference%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20type%20of%20ads%20you%20receive%20may%20be%20adjustable%20in%20your%20settings.%20But%20for%20most%20platforms%2C%20you%20won't%20be%20able%20to%20control%20how%20many%20you%20see.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-ads-adwords%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETo%20personalize%20Google%20ads%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20for%20example%2C%20you%20can%20go%20to%20%26quot%3BMy%20Ad%20Center%26quot%3B%20and%20opt%20to%20turn%20personalized%20ads%20on%20or%20off%20in%20the%20top-right%20corner.%20If%20you%20turn%20them%20on%2C%20Google%20will%20use%20the%20information%20it%20collects%20about%20you%20to%20give%20you%20more%20personalized%20ads.%20That%20means%20your%20activity%20on%20Google%20sites%20and%20apps%20will%20be%20saved%20in%20your%20Google%20Account%20and%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-does-google-know-about-me-search-history-delete-2019-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20information%20from%20your%20account%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20like%20your%20age%2C%20will%20also%20be%20used.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20decided%20to%20keep%20personalized%20ads%20off%20for%20Google%20because%20that's%20how%20I%20usually%20have%20it.%20This%20resulted%20in%20me%20sometimes%20missing%20ads%20on%20my%20screen.%20I'm%20so%20used%20to%20seeing%20random%20photos%20and%20brand%20names%20in%20the%20corners%20and%20sides%20of%20my%20screen%20that%20my%20eyes%20glazed%20over%20some%20of%20them.%20It%20drew%20a%20sharp%20contrast%20to%20my%20experience%20with%20social%20media%20ads%2C%20which%20are%20fully%20personalized%20to%20my%20activity%20on%20and%20off-site%20and%20often%20pull%20my%20attention.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20comes%20to%20social%20media%2C%20you%20don't%20have%20as%20much%20of%20a%20choice%20%E2%80%94%20although%20some%20do%20let%20you%20pay%20to%20remove%20or%20decrease%20ads.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhelp%2F262038446684066%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFacebook%20now%20offers%20a%20paid%20version%20in%20the%20EU%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20people%20who%20prefer%20an%20ad-free%20experience%2C%20YouTube%20lets%20you%20pay%20for%20Premium%20to%20remove%20them%2C%20and%20Elon%20Musk's%20X%20says%20paying%20for%20X%20Premium%2B%20means%20no%20ads%20in%20your%20For%20You%20or%20Following%20feeds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20TikTok%2C%20for%20example%2C%20says%20on%20its%20website%20that%20%26quot%3Byou%20will%20always%20see%20ads%20based%20on%20what%20you%20do%20on%20Tik