%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22India%20Stocks%2C%20Bonds%20Set%20To%20Gain%20As%20Exit%20Polls%20Predict%20Landslide%20BJP%20Win%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndian%20stocks%2C%20bonds%2C%20and%20the%20rupee%20are%20poised%20to%20climb%20on%20Monday%20after%20exit%20polls%20indicated%20a%20resounding%20victory%20for%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20polls%20suggest%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party-led%20alliance%20will%20clinch%20substantially%20more%20seats%20than%20the%20272%20required%20for%20a%20majority%20in%20the%20543-seat%20lower%20house%20of%20Parliament.%20The%20votes%20will%20be%20counted%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20predictions%20are%20likely%20to%20calm%20investors%20rattled%20by%20recent%20stock%20market%20volatility%2C%20driven%20by%20concerns%20that%20the%20BJP%20might%20fall%20well%20short%20of%20PM%20Modi's%20ambitious%20400-seat%20target%20due%20to%20low%20voter%20turnouts%20and%20tight%20races%20in%20several%20states.%20A%20landslide%20win%20would%20enable%20the%20party%20to%20push%20through%20policies%20that%20are%20seen%20as%20crucial%20for%20boosting%20India's%20economic%20growth%2C%20which%20is%20already%20among%20the%20world's%20fastest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20was%20some%20skepticism%2C%20with%20volatility%20picking%20up%20as%20some%20people%20were%20getting%20jittery%20on%20the%20election%20outcome.%20Now%20it%20will%20settle%20-%20this%20is%20a%20resounding%20vote%20for%20continuity%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Vinit%20Sambre%2C%20who%20oversees%20about%20%2412%20billion%20as%20head%20of%20equities%20at%20DSP%20Mutual%20Fund%20in%20Mumbai.%20%26quot%3BMarkets%20could%20react%20positively%20on%20Monday.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fra2qvm3o_gfx-1_625x