Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Baroda-born%20cricketer%20isn't%20someone%20who%20takes%20his%20success%20too%20seriously%2C%20and%20the%20same%20goes%20for%20the%20unsuccessful%20periods%20he%20goes%20through.%20He%20admitted%20that%20the%20only%20way%20to%20get%20out%20of%20the%20rut%20is%20to%20accept%20that%20he%20needs%20to%20be%20better%20at%20some%20skills%20and%20work%20on%20them%20to%20improve.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20take%20my%20successes%20too%20seriously.%20Whatever%20I%20have%20done%20well%2C%20I%20have%20forgotten%20about%20them%20immediately%20and%20moved%20forward.%20Same%20with%20difficult%20times%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20run%20away%20from%20it.%20I%20face%20everything%20with%20%5Bmy%5D%20chin%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20they%20say%2C%20this%20too%20shall%20pass.%20So%20coming%20out%20%5Bof%20these%20phases%5D%20is%20simple%3A%20just%20play%20the%20sport%2C%20accept%20that%20%5Byou%20need%20to%5D%20maybe%20get%20better%20at%20your%20skillset%2C%20keep%20working%20hard%20-%20hard%20work%20never%20goes%20to%20waste%20-%20and%20keep%20smiling%2C%26quot%3B%20Hardik%20concluded.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717305480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fddgn296g_hardik-pandya_625x300_02_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ft20-world-cup-2024%2Fthis-too-shall-pass-hardik-pandya-opens-up-on-difficult-times-before-t20-world-cup-2024-5798062%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Hardik%20Pandya%20opened%20up%20on%20the%20recent%20'difficult%20times'%20in%20his%20career%20as%20he%20roars%20back%20to%20form%20with%20the%20Indian%20team%20in%20T20%20World%20Cup%202024.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ft20-world-cup-2024%2Fthis-too-shall-pass-hardik-pandya-opens-up-on-difficult-times-before-t20-world-cup-2024-5798062%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fs