0residents%20of%20Chennai%20was%20on%2019%20June%202019%20when%20the%20city%20was%20out%20of%20drinking%20water.%20Called%20%E2%80%98Day%20Zero%E2%80%99%2C%20it%20was%20one%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F349257%2Fbengaluru-residents-water-crisis-rainwater-harvesting-gardening-in-summer-rohit-malekar-suma-raj%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eworst%20water%20crises%3C%2Fa%3E%20faced%20by%20the%20city%20as%20the%20municipality%20ran%20out%20of%20drinking%20water.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAround%20the%20same%20time%2C%20Prashant%20Sharma%2C%20a%20programme%20manager%20in%20an%20IT%20firm%2C%20happened%20to%20be%20visiting%20his%20in-laws%20in%20Chennai%20with%20his%20wife%20and%20two-year-old%20son.%20The%20worried%20father%20had%20to%20scramble%20for%20water%20for%20over%20a%20week%20to%20provide%20for%20his%20toddler%E2%80%99s%20needs.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20recalls%20how%20people%20rushed%20towards%20the%20water%20tankers%20and%20paid%20extra%20to%20ensure%20that%20they%20received%20it.%20However%2C%20the%20water%20they%20got%20was%20often%20salty%20and%20unclean%20which%20needed%20to%20be%20boiled%20several%20times%20before%20being%20used.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20incident%20left%20him%20spending%20days%20in%20search%20of%20solutions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20wondered%20about%20what%20we%20could%20do.%20Since%20water%20is%20a%20finite%20resource%2C%20how%20could%20we%20make%20its%20usage%20more%20circular%3F%E2%80%9D%20Prashant%20shares%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20solution%20the%2050-year-old%20found%20was%20using%20greywater%2C%20which%20is%20basically%20domestic%20wastewater%20from%20wash%20basins%2C%20washing%20machines%2C%20showers%2C%20kitchens.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20DowntoEarth%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.downtoearth.or