aced%20considerable%20obstacles%20during%20his%20academic%20journey.%20Struggling%20with%20certain%20subjects%2C%20he%20found%20himself%20having%20to%20retake%20exams%2C%20extending%20his%20engineering%20programme%20to%20six%20years.%20After%20four%20years%2C%20he%20encountered%20a%20dilemma%20%E2%80%94%20lacking%20his%20degree%20yet%20unable%20to%20disclose%20this%20to%20his%20parents.%20In%20a%20stroke%20of%20resourcefulness%2C%20he%20secured%20a%20position%20at%20Ericsson%20India%20in%20Gurugram%20through%20a%20friend%2C%20earning%20Rs%209%2C000%20per%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20here%20in%20November%202014%20that%20the%20entrepreneur%20had%20his%20first%20bite%20of%20pizza%20with%20his%20friends%2C%20which%20changed%20his%20life%20forever.%20%E2%80%9CI%20loved%20the%20taste%20of%20the%20pizza%20and%20wondered%20how%20it%20was%20made.%20It%20seemed%20to%20be%20a%20fatter%20version%20of%20a%20%3Cem%3Eroti%20%3C%2Fem%3Ewith%20a%20different%20sauce%20and%20cheese%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sandeep%20recalls%20in%20a%20conversation%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20next%20few%20months%2C%20the%20idea%20of%20starting%20a%20food%20business%20crept%20into%20his%20mind.%20But%20how%20does%20one%20make%20a%20pizza%20and%20build%20a%20business%20around%20the%20same%3F%20To%20learn%20the%20nitty%20gritty%20of%20such%20a%20business%2C%20he%20approached%20a%20few%20pizza%20outlets%20in%20Gurugram%20and%20Haryana.%20It%20was%20Pizza%20Wings%20in%20Rohtak%20where%20he%20got%20a%20chance%20to%20learn%20the%20ABCs%20of%20running%20a%20pizza%20store.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20trained%20for%20about%20a%20month%20and%20a%20half%20at%20Pizza%20Wings.%20They%20taught%20me%20everything%20from%20how%20to%20make%20the%20dough%20and%20the%20sauce%20to%20how%20to%20deliver%20the%20pizza%20and%20run%20a%20store.%20I%20realised%20that%20making%20a%20pizza%20is%20not%20rocket%20science%2C%E2%80%9D%20laughs%20Sandeep.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUpon%20completing%20his%20training%2C%20Sandeep%20returned%20home%20and%20shared%20his%20ambitious%20business%20plan%20with%20his%20family%20%E2%80%94%20opening%20a%20pizza%20shop%20in%20the%20bustling%20city%20centre.%20However%2C%20his%20father%20was%20reluctant%20to%20invest%20in%20the%20venture.%20Undeterred%2C%20Sandeep%20sought%20support%20from%20his%20brother%20and%20friends%2C%20who%20collectively%20contributed%20the%20initial%20investment%20of%20Rs%206.5%20lakh%20to%20establish%20his%20inaugural%20store%20in%20Gohana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC61bd2stDl0%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC61bd2stDl0%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC61bd2stDl0%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20Pizza%20Galleria%20(%40pizzagalleria_india)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20father%20was%20upset%20about%20me%20quitting%20and%20returning.%20He%20expected%20me%20to%20make%20a%20name%20for%20myself%20as%20an%20engineer%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Sandeep.%20While%20convincing%20his%20family%20was%20a%20big%20challenge%2C%20the%20next%20challenge%20was%20finding%20skilled%20labour%20for%20the%20store%20in%20a%20city%20where%20many%20hadn%E2%80%99t%20tasted%20a%20pizza.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20hired%20three%20boys%20who%20had%20completed%20Class%2012%20and%20trusted%20my%20vision.%20I%20taught%20them%20how%20to%20make%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F249937%2Fgujarat-ahmedabad-jashuben-shah-old-pizza-best-food-dominos-pizza-hut-women-entrepreneur-success-him16%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epizza%20base%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20sauce%2C%20pack%20the%20pizzas%20for%20service%20as%20well%20as%20delivery%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%20CEO%20of%20Pizza%20Galleria.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20and%20most%20crucial%20step%20was%20to%20create%20awareness%20and%20market%20the%20product.%20For%20this%2C%20Sandeep%20rode%20his%20bike%20around%20the%20city%2C%20knocking%20on%20doors%20and%20distributing%20pamphlets.%20He%20also%20carried%20a%20mike%20and%20speaker%20and%20went%20around%20announcing%2C%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%98Khul%20gaya%2C%20khul%20gaya%2C%20ab%20aapke%20sheher%20mein%20Pizza%20Galleria%20khul%20gaya%20%3C%2Fem%3E(Pizza%20Galleria%20is%20now%20open%20in%20your%20town%2Fcity)%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20practice%20is%20followed%20by%20him%20even%20today.%20Every%20time%20a%20new%20store%20opens%2C%20he%20rides%20around%20the%20city%20shouting%20these%20slogans%2C%20followed%20by%20distributing%20pamphlets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ED-day%20arrived%20on%2025%20December%202015%2C%20when%20many%20people%20in%20Gohana%20tasted%20their%20first%20fresh-dough%20pizza.%20To%20entice%20customers%2C%20he%20offered%20the%20first%20300%20pizzas%20free%2C%20a%20practice%20followed%20even%20today%20at%20all%20new%20outlets.%20Slowly%20and%20steadily%2C%20thanks%20to%20the%20ambience%20and%20novelty%20of%20pizzas%2C%20a%20loyal%20customer%20base%20was%20created.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20started%20with%20a%20limited%20menu%20of%20seven%20to%20eight%20pizzas%2C%20garlic%20bread%2C%20and%20some%20pasta.%20It%20took%20almost%20a%20year%20for%20Sandeep%E2%80%99s%20pizza%20venture%20to%20taste%20success%20in%20Gohana.%20The%20biggest%20challenge%2C%20he%20explains%2C%20was%20teaching%20people%20to%20try%20a%20new%20dish.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPeople%20didn%E2%80%99t%20know%20what%E2%80%99s%20so%20special%20about%20a%20fresh%20dough%20pizza%20or%20even%20how%20to%20eat%20it.%20Just%20like%20me%2C%20they%20too%20thought%20of%20it%20like%20a%20fat%20%3Cem%3Eroti%20%3C%2Fem%3Ewith%20a%20different%20%3Cem%3Echutney%20%3C%2Fem%3E(sauce).%20I%20also%20had%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20quality%20of%20the%20food%20was%20perfect%20in%20the%20absence%20of%20experienced%20chefs%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20overcame%20this%20challenge%20by%20building%20Standard%20Operating%20Procedures%20(SOPs)%20to%20be%20followed%20for%20making%20the%20pizzas%2C%20and%20then%20serving%2C%20packing%2C%20and%20delivering%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ECreating%20employment%20in%20small%20towns%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEventually%2C%20as%20the%20people%20of%20Gohana%20accepted%20and%20thronged%20to%20Pizza%20Galleria%2C%20Sandeep%20knew%20he%20was%20on%20the%20right%20track.%20This%20led%20him%20to%20open%20the%20next%20store%20in%20Panipat%20and%20Ganaur%20(Haryana)%20in%202017.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201080px)%20100vw%2C%201080px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fsandeep-1716813220.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sandeep%20with%20his%20team%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%