emic%20to%20ensure%20access%20to%20healthcare%20in%20remote%20Ladakh%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Vishwadeep%20Trust%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fguna-organics-1716443053.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20team%20of%20Vishwadeep%20Trust%20conducts%20drives%20to%20educate%20the%20people%20of%20Ladakh%20against%20plastic%20and%20litter%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fguna-organics-1716443053.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fguna-organics-1716443053-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fguna-organics-1716443053-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fguna-organics-1716443053-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fguna-organics-1716443053-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-350873%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20team%20of%20Vishwadeep%20Trust%20conducts%20drives%20to%20educate%20the%20people%20of%20Ladakh%20against%20plastic%20and%20litter%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Vishwadeep%20Trust%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlong%20the%20way%2C%20there%20have%20been%20multiple%20boosts%20to%20her%20efforts%2C%20sometimes%20in%20the%20form%20of%20people%E2%80%99s%20support%2C%20and%20other%20times%20in%20the%20form%20of%20mentorship%20opportunities.%20The%20most%20significant%2C%20she%20recalls%2C%20is%20being%20a%20part%20of%20the%20cohort%20of%20the%20Women%20Entrepreneurship%20Platform%20(WEP)%20%E2%80%94%20a%20first-of-its-kind%2C%20unified%20access%20portal%20incubate