%20and%20vegetables%20of%20consistent%20quality%20in%20the%20next%20season%20and%20of%20course%2C%20save%20money%20and%20become%20self-reliant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESurat-based%20home%20gardener%20Anupama%20Desai%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CSometimes%20it%20becomes%20very%20difficult%20for%20us%20to%20know%20the%20quality%2C%20age%2C%20or%20if%20there%20is%20any%20kind%20of%20chemical%20coating%20on%20seeds%20available%20in%20the%20market.%20Once%20purchased%2C%20you%20cannot%20return%20them.%20So%20it%20is%20better%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F346317%2Fassam-organic-farmer-neelam-dutta-conserves-climate-resilient-heirloom-seeds-pabhoi-greens-northeast%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estore%20seeds%20%3C%2Fa%3Efrom%20your%20garden%2C%20as%20there%20is%20no%20compromise%20on%20their%20health.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20past%2014%20years%2C%20she%20has%20been%20growing%20seasonal%20vegetables%20and%20has%20been%20collecting%20seeds%20of%20most%20of%20the%20produce%20grown%20at%20home.%20%E2%80%9CBelieve%20me%2C%20storing%20seeds%20at%20home%20makes%20your%20gardening%20work%20very%20easy.%20It%20does%20not%20require%20a%20lot%20of%20effort%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%2056-year-old%20gardener.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20conversation%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20Anupama%20shares%2010%20easy%20tips%20to%20store%20seeds%20in%20summer%20to%20be%20able%20to%20sow%20them%20in%20the%20next%20season.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EYou%20can%20store%20seeds%20of%20watermelon%2C%20muskmelon%2C%20%3Cem%3Egalka%20%3C%2Fem%3E(sponge%20gourd)%2C%20pumpkin%2C%20%3Cem%3Evalor%20papdi%20%3C%2Fem%3E(field%20beans)%2C%20and%20%3Cem%3Ekakdi%3C%2Fem%3E%20(Armenian%20cucumber)%2C%20etc%20in%20this%20season%20(May-end).%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EBoth%20watermelon%20and%20muskmelon%20are%20fruit%20plants%20and%20can%20easily%20be%20grown%20on%20terraces.%20A