%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERaji%20shares%20that%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20challenges%20in%20the%20cloud%20kitchen%20business%20is%20establishing%20brand%20visibility%20and%20attracting%20customers%20without%20a%20physical%20storefront.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COvercoming%20this%20involves%20investing%20in%20a%20strong%20online%20presence%2C%20leveraging%20social%20media%2C%20partnering%20with%20food%20delivery%20platforms%2C%20and%20offering%20promotions%20to%20incentivise%20first-time%20orders.%20Maintain%20consistency%20and%20on-time%20delivery%20for%20a%20better%20customer%20response%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20operate%20a%20cloud%20kitchen%20in%20India%2C%20you%20need%20an%20FSSAI%20Food%20Safety%20And%20Standards%20Authority%20License%2C%20GST%20Registration%2C%20Health%20Licence%2C%20Fire%20and%20Safety%20License%2C%20and%20a%20Trade%20License.%20You%20can%20read%20more%20about%20the%20documents%20needed%20for%20applying%20for%20these%20licenses%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbingage.com%2Fblog%2Flicences-required-to-start-a-cloud-kitchen-in-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20All%20images%20credit%3A%20Raji%20and%20Anjum)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716558724000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fparvej-khan-2-1716558045.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D351113%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Raji%20Sakthi%20and%20Naaz%20Anjum%2C%20successful%20cloud%20kitchen%20owners%20from%20Kerala%20and%20Telangana%2C%20share%20insights%20on%20how%20to%20run%20a%20food%20business.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Tina%20Freese%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F351113%2Fhow-to-start-a-cloud-kitchen-licensing-marketing-owners-raji-sakthi-naaz-anjum-share-tips